1. Name html/img files in lowercase

2. For html: Put '#' in uncertain place, so that we can directy search # to modify.
e.g. <a href="#.html">; <img src="img/#.jpg" ...>
And remember to replace all '#' in the end.


3. php template

	1)top menu:
<?php
require('topnav.php');
?>
	
	2)top menu+search box:
<?php
require('topbar.php');
?>
	
	3)footer:
<?php
require('footer.php');
?>
	
	4)sidebar:
<?php
require('sidebar.php');
?>